{"tid":1535072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日都唔肯罷工既你地，我屌哂你地老未冚家剷！","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:41:19.000Z","uid":160887,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa832af2ca9bad31783e4cc2ffb7484857f434a","tid":1535072,"uid":160887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"五大訴求呢，未解決！<br />\n女義士爆眼，未解決！<br />\n女士被輪姦，未解決！<br />\n義士被虐打，未解決！<br />\n太子站死人，未解決！<br />\n警察濫用暴力，未解決！<br />\n<br />\n我係咁以都數到幾樣野<br />\n叫你罷工就牙痛咁款<br />\n搵錢係咪咁重要？<br />\n<br />\n個個都得把口，話幾唔想送中<br />\n得星期六日行出嚟，就以為自己做緊好多<br />\n咁你星期一至五咪比緊時間差佬重新部署囉<br />\n<br />\n大佬，而家打緊仗啊<br />\n有冇得同人講話星期一至五要休戰<br />\n星期六日先再開個拖？<br />\n你都戇撚鳩<br />\n<br />\n你怕俾人清算呀嘛<br />\n你人多企出嚟，佢係咪炒得哂先？<br />\n<br />\n自己反省下啦，咪靠撚哂學生<br />\n講到學生先怕比人送中咁<br />\n屌你老未"},{"pid":"4de7ca6a422dc417b98eb2ad3ac1a1cff139f79e","tid":1535072,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:21:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e46eed8ac0c09bbca3f910f95d6200cb168b48